{"tid":2216752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"昨日東突，今日圖博，明日香港","createTime":"2020-09-25T02:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T03:20:52.000Z","uid":188515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5cbf36d00d0c7d9bcb100f5a220b5b47b11455","tid":2216752,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:52:34.000Z","msg":"中共恐怖統治境內少數民族，令新疆維族人、藏人在過著水深火熱的生活。華府智「詹姆斯頓基金會」（Jamestown Foundation）周二（22日）發表報告指出，中國正強制西藏（圖博）農民和牧民參與勞動計劃，這些措施類似在新疆實施的強制「職業訓練」。<br />\n法新社報導，西藏位於中國偏遠西部，人口以佛教徒為主，這項計劃把當地鄉村的勞工轉至工廠就業。西藏當局誇耀稱，這項計劃是脫貧手段，與中國領導人習近平提出的2020年全中國脫貧目標一致。<br />\n但詹姆斯頓基金會的研究人員們表示，這些「軍隊化的職業訓練」也是對藏族進行「意識形態灌輸及同化」的一種形式。因為西藏人口有90%是藏族。<br />\n報告警告，這些措施恐會在政治敏感的西藏地區造成「文化遺產喪失」。<br />\n報告提到，2020年的1至7月，西藏有超過50萬名鄉村勞工（被）接受培訓，這些人主要是牧民及自給自足的農民。每個地區、縣都有設定最低受訓人數。<br />\n法新社續指，這項報告雖未提出前幾年的任何可供比較數據，但根據報告援引的一項2019年中國政府行動計劃指出，這些職訓計畫旨在逐漸灌輸（藏人）「工作紀律、漢語和工作倫理」。<br />\n報告提及，達到「工人聘用」配額（培訓藏人人數達標）的企業，最多可獲得50萬元人民幣（約214.16萬元台幣）。這項計劃還鼓勵當地農民和牧民，把他們的牲口及土地轉讓給大型的中國國營合作社。<br />\n報告作者鄭國恩（Adrian Zenz）直言：「在中國政府日益同化少數民族政策的脈絡下，這些政策很可能會導致語言、文化和精神遺產被消滅。」鄭國恩是德國人類學家，因其對新疆再教育營的研究而知名。他也是美國「共產主義受難者紀念基金會」的中國問題資深研究員<br />\n報告指稱，將近5萬人已被轉移到西藏各地，有3000多人被送往中國其他地區。這與新疆地區的強制勞動計劃類似。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s850HMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs850HMM.png&h=579f6a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bg8p9rQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbg8p9rQ.png&h=092888b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zySqTTF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzySqTTF.png&h=29e05b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200923/K4ATKBEQ2JB6ZK3PUDYUVSYALM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200923%2FK4ATKBEQ2JB6ZK3PUDYUVSYALM%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOhePMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=f3b4c98b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200923%2FK4ATKBEQ2JB6ZK3PUDYUVSYALM%2F&h=2255f5b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200923/K4ATKBEQ2JB6ZK3PUDYUVSYALM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcc5383074cc53201d9888c4197a5a0c1cc472d","tid":2216752,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"順便一推<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VYDeVippl_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVYDeVippl_c&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOhePMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a1b301f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VYDeVippl_c</a>"},{"pid":"5c54d4a78269fe822220033e01d837b26eeaf096","tid":2216752,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba8bc65fb956fef294f30434a7609eb5a80240f9","tid":2216752,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:20:52.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"0bcc5383074cc53201d9888c4197a5a0c1cc472d","tid":2216752,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"順便一推<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VYDeVippl_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVYDeVippl_c&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOhePMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a1b301f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VYDeVippl_c</a>"}}